C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAbout%20200%20ski%20patrollers%20are%20on%20strike%20for%20better%20wages%20at%20Utah's%20Park%20City%20Mountain%20Resort.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELarge%20swaths%20of%20the%20mountain%20have%20been%20closed%2C%20and%20lift%20lines%20have%20been%20long%2C%20frustrating%20customers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20customers%20told%20BI%20they%20won't%20return%20to%20corporate%20resorts%2C%20instead%20opting%20for%20family-run%20spots.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESkiers%20at%20Utah's%20Park%20City%20Mountain%20Resort%20say%20their%20vacations%20were%20spent%20waiting%20in%20painfully%20long%20lines%20and%20navigating%20overcrowded%20trails%20after%20hundreds%20of%20ski%20patrollers%20and%20mountain%20safety%20personnel%20walked%20off%20the%20job.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20stoppage%20over%20wages%20at%20one%20of%20the%20nation's%20largest%20ski%20resorts%20came%20as%20more%20than%20two%20feet%20of%20snow%20blanketed%20Park%20City%20in%20the%20last%20week%20%E2%80%94%20normally%2C%20a%20skier's%20dream.%20But%20for%20Jim%20Lebenthal%2C%20the%20snow%20was%20mostly%20experienced%20from%20the%20back%20of%20a%20line.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20started%20out%20bad%2C%20and%20it%20got%20worse%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lebenthal%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20a%20wealth%20management%20firm.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELebenthal%2C%20also%20a%20CNBC%20contributor%2C%20said%20that%2075%25%20of%20the%20mountain%20was%20closed%20on%20his%20family's%20first%20day%20of%20skiing%20on%20December%2027.%20By%20December%2030%2C%20he%20said%2080%25%20of%20the%20mountain%20was%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20lift%20lines%20were%20interminable%2C%26quot%3B%20Lebenthal%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20got%20to%20the%20point%20where%20it%20was%20one%20run%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20a%20run%20takes%20probably%20seven%20minutes%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20that%20is%20sitting%20in%20lift%20lines.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETF%20Jenkins%2C%20a%20managing%20director%20at%20a%20Florida-based%20wealth%20management%20firm%2C%20said%20the%20closures%20resulted%20in%20limited%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20wasn't%20a%20ton%20of%20terrain%20open%2C%20and%20we%20were%20just%20doing%20the%20same%20thing%20over%20and%20over%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Jenkins%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20resort%20guests%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20complain%20about%20the%20conditions.%20Vail%20Resorts%20Inc.%2C%20which%20owns%20the%20resort%2C%20saw%20its%20stock%20drop%20about%206%25%20in%20the%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208715ffa-76cd-4aaf-962d-0b32572feefb%5C%22%3EA%20strike%20during%20peak%20ski%20season%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Park%20City%20Professional%20Ski%20Patrol%20Association%20(PCPSPA)%20said%20it%20has%20been%20in%20contract%20negotiations%20with%20Vail%20Resorts%20since%20April%20and%20is%20trying%20to%20secure%20wage%20increases%20to%20match%20inflation%2C%20among%20other%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20200%20ski%20patrollers%2C%20represented%20by%20the%20union%2C%20went%20on%20strike%20on%20December%2027%20after%20negotiations%20with%20Vail%20Resorts%20broke%20down.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20resort%20remained%20open%2C%20%26quot%3Bwith%20safety%20as%20its%20top%20priority%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20resort%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22972%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hundreds%20of%20skiers%20and%20snowboarders%20wait%20in%20line%20at%20a%20lift.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6779bbc49de00e389eb460b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22729%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESkiers%20and%20snowboarders%20waited%20in%20hour-long%20lines%20at%20lifts.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20TF%20Jenkins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20from%20the%20resort%20told%20BI%20that%20December%2030%20was%20%26quot%3Bespecially%20challenging%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20early%20season%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEach%20day%2C%20we%20open%20the%20terrain%20we%20can%20safely%20open%20with%20the%20team%20members%20we%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Sara%20Huey%2C%20Vail%20Resorts'%20Director%20of%20Community%20and%20Government%20Affairs%2C%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20had%20impacts%20to%20terrain%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20patrol%20strike.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2212dc4d42-beac-4f4d-ac24-d4b33f894143%5C%22%3EThe%20union's%20demands%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVail%20Resorts%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20it%20had%20reached%20agreements%20on%2024%20out%20of%2027%20contract%20terms.%20The%20remaining%20issues%20were%20contract%20length%2C%20wages%2C%20and%20benefits%20%E2%80%94%20often%20considered%20by%20members%20to%20be%20the%20most%20important%20parts%20of%20a%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBill%20Rock%2C%20the%20President%20of%20Vail%20Resorts'%20Mountain%20Division%2C%20said%20the%20resort%20has%20made%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20investments%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20wages%20and%20benefits%20are%20strong%2C%20as%20demonstrated%20by%20the%20high%20return%20rate%20among%20patrol%20teams%20across%20our%20company%20and%20by%20the%20number%20of%20applicants%20we%20get%20for%20any%20patrol%20opening%2C%26quot%3B%20Rock%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20doesn't%20match%20up%20with%20the%20lived%20experiences%20of%20ski%20patrollers%2C%20said%20Margaux%20Klingensmith%2C%20a%20business%20manager%20for%20the%20union%20and%20six-year%20patroller%20at%20Park%20City%20Mountain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20patrollers%20who%20cannot%20afford%20to%20continue%20doing%20this%20job%20if%20they%20are%20not%20compensated%20better%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Klingensmith%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20wants%20patroller%20base%20pay%20raised%20from%20%2421%20to%20%2423%20with%20an%20included%20cost-of-living%20adjustment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20wants%20to%20combat%20wage%20compression%2C%20which%20Klingensmith%20said%20has%20allowed%20five-year%20patrollers%20to%20be%20making%20the%20same%20amount%20as%2015-year%20patrollers%2C%20who%20are%20significantly%20more%20experienced.%20Better%20compensation%20would%20help%20retain%20those%20experienced%20patrollers%2C%20which%20Klingensmith%20said%20the%20resort%20is%20losing%20%26quot%3Bat%20an%20atrocious%20rate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrying%20to%20keep%20that%20experience%20around%20with%20a%20better%20compensation%20package%20is%20the%20real%20goal.%20But%20overall%2C%20the%20reason%20we're%20fighting%20for%20this%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20have%20members%20of%20our%20unit%20able%20to%20afford%20groceries%20and%20afford%20to%20pay%20their%20rent%2C%26quot%3B%20Klingensmith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20is%20also%20seeking%20better%20benefits%20for%20its%20members%2C%20including%20a%20healthcare%20stipend%2C%20accruing%20paid%20time%20off%2C%20and%20parental%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Striking%20ski%20patrollers%20hold%20signs.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6779bc2c9de00e389eb460ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESpirits%20at%20the%20picket%20line%20have%20been%20high%20as%20the%20strike%20stretches%20into%20its%20second%20week.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Margaux%20Klingensmith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227d7311bf-b874-40a5-8847-e8fe03747bce%5C%22%3ECustomers%20say%20they%20won't%20be%20back%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PCPSPA%20said%20its%20members%20unanimously%20passed%20a%20strike%20authorization%20vote%20on%20December%2013.%20In%20the%20days%20following%2C%20Deirdra%20Walsh%2C%20the%20VP%20and%20COO%20of%20Park%20City%20Mountain%2C%20issued%20several%20statements%20on%20Park%20City's%20website%20stating%20that%20the%20mountain%20would%20remain%20open%20%26quot%3Bregardless%20of%20the%20union's%20actions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20customers%20told%20BI%20that%20they%20felt%20Vail%20Resorts%20did%20not%20effectively%20communicate%20to%20them%20that%20their%20visit%20could%20be%20impacted%20by%20a%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20should%20have%20let%20us%20know%20that%20this%20was%20potentially%20going%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lebenthal%2C%20who%20added%20that%20he%20would%20seek%20a%20refund%20if%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJenkins%20also%20said%20he%20was%20frustrated%20by%20what%20he%20called%20a%20lack%20of%20communication%20from%20Vail%20Resorts.%20Jenkins%2C%20who%20bought%20four-day%20passes%20for%20his%20family%20eight%20months%20in%20advance%2C%20said%20he%20has%20reached%20out%20several%20times%20for%20a%20refund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJenkins%20added%20that%20there%20were%20also%20communication%20issues%20regarding%20wait%20times%20for%20the%20lifts.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20give%20you%20the%20wait%20times%20on%20the%20app%20for%20each%20lift%20that%20was%20open%2C%20and%20it%20would%20say%20five%20minutes%2C%20and%20you'd%20get%20there%2C%20and%20it'd%20be%20like%2040%20minutes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it's%20common%20for%20mountains%20to%20be%20crowded%2C%20but%20this%20week's%20experience%20at%20Park%20City%20turned%20into%20a%20safety%20issue%20with%20skiers%20of%20varying%20levels%20zipping%20down%20crowded%20trails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20human-created%20situation%20without%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20communication.%20I%20mean%2C%20we%20would've%20been%20fine%20sitting%20in%20and%20playing%20games%20all%20day%20if%20it%20was%20just%20not%20great%20snow%20and%20not%20great%20weather%2C%20but%20it%20was%20more%20frustrating%20when%20it's%20created%20by%20two%20different%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20Jenkins%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20kind%20of%20been%20a%20zero-sum%20game.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20Jenkins%20said%20he%20will%20only%20ski%20at%20smaller%2