d%20Scholz%20an%20%26quot%3Bincompetent%20fool%26quot%3B%20and%20signaled%20his%20support%20for%20Germany's%20AfD%20party.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20a%20new%20interview%2C%20Scholz%20said%20he%20was%20concerned%20about%20Musk%20backing%20the%20AfD.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGerman%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20responded%20to%20criticism%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-afd-germany-far-right-party-immigration-election-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20new%20interview%20with%20a%20German%20magazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%20published%20in%20Stern%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Scholz%20said%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20new%26quot%3B%20about%20criticism%20from%20%26quot%3Brich%20media%20entrepreneurs%20who%20do%20not%20appreciate%20social%20democratic%20politics%20and%20do%20not%20hide%20their%20opinions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bkeep%20your%20cool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20people%20on%20social%20media%20who%20want%20to%20attract%20attention%20with%20strong%20slogans%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BThe%20rule%20is%3A%20Don't%20feed%20the%20troll.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20found%20it%20%26quot%3Bfar%20more%20concerning%26quot%3B%20that%20Musk%20supported%20%26quot%3Ba%20partly%20far-right%20party%20like%20the%20AfD%2C%20which%20advocates%20rapprochement%20with%20Putin's%20Russia%20and%20seeks%20to%20weaken%20transatlantic%20relations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20sparked%20debate%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-in-germany-struggled-berlin-loves-living-in-dresden-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGermany%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20weeks%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-sparks-backlash-germany-weighs-in-on-politics-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_b