that%20Dibil%20Kumar%20B%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Anchal%20who%20was%2028%20at%20the%20time%20and%20served%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army's%2045%20AD%20Regiment%20in%20Pathankot%2C%20was%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20Ranjini.%20After%20the%20twins%20were%20born%20on%20January%2024%2C%202006%2C%20however%2C%20he%20began%20distancing%20himself%20from%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unwed%20mother%20then%20approached%20the%20Kerala%20State%20Women's%20Commission%2C%20which%20ordered%20a%20test%20to%20establish%20the%20paternity%20of%20the%20twins.%20This%20infuriated%20Kumar%2C%20who%20allegedly%20began%20plotting%20her%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECBI%20officials%20said%20that%20Rajesh%20P%2C%20who%20was%2033%20at%20the%20time%20and%20also%20served%20with%20Kumar%20in%20the%20same%20Army%20regiment%2C%20befriended%20Ranjini%20and%20her%20mother.%20He%20assured%20them%20that%20he%20would%20help%20convince%20Kumar%20to%20marry%20Ranjini%2C%20but%20allegedly%20joined%20in%20the%20plot%20to%20kill%20her%20and%20her%20daughters%20instead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManhunt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20and%20Rajesh%20went%20on%20the%20run%20soon%20after%20the%20crime%20and%20were%20declared%20deserters%20by%20the%20Army%20in%20March%202006.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20extensive%20investigations%20by%20local%20police%20and%20a%20reward%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20for%20information%20that%20would%20lead%20to%20their%20capture%2C%20there%20was%20no%20sign%20of%20the%20two%20men.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20CBI%20in%202010%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20Kerala%20High%20Court%2C%20but%20a%20breakthrough%20eluded%20the%20agency%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhole%20New%20Lives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAfter%20years%20of%20pursuit%2C%20the%20CBI%20received%20a%20tip-off%20that%20Kumar%20and%20Rajesh%20were%20living%20in%20Puducherry%20under%20fake%20names%20and%20had%20manage