-namibia-desert-transformed-by-rain-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erainy%20landscapes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Whatever%20the%20reason%20for%20his%20choice%2C%20we%20were%20bound%20for%20the%20Emerald%20City.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20arrived%20in%20Seattle%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20different%20side%20of%20my%20son%2C%20a%20quiet%20confidence%20that%20is%20often%20overshadowed%20by%20the%20chaos%20of%20daily%20life%20and%20squabbles%20with%20his%20brother.%20It%20took%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20for%20him%20to%20stop%20asking%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20we%20doing%20next%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20believe%20me%20when%20I%20told%20him%20that%20we%20could%20do%20whatever%20he%20wanted.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20selected%20our%20meals%20and%20set%20our%20schedule%2C%20and%20we%20lingered%20for%20as%20long%20as%20he%20wanted%20at%20his%20favorite%20places%20%E2%80%94%20the%20top%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamous-buildings-you-need-to-see-in-your-lifetime-2016-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20Space%20Needle%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20among%20the%20sculptures%20of%20the%20Chihuly%20exhibit%2C%20among%20the%20fishmongers%20flinging%20their%20catch%20at%20Pike%20Place%20Market.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fb7aef54-0e60-42e1-b620-71e5008e60c2%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20felt%20different%20than%20a%20regular%20vacation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20charmed%20by%20the%20things%20my%20son%20found%20interesting%20and%20the%20details%20he%20noticed.%20Walking%20in%20the%20rain%20back%20to%20our%20hotel%20one%20afternoon%2C%20I%20was%20struck%20by%20how%20different%20it%20felt%20from%20our%20usual%20family%20vacations.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThose%20trips%20are%20wonderful%20in%20their%20own%20way%2C%20but%20they%20often%20involve%20a%20lot%20of%20compromise%20and%20ju