eports%20of%20a%20surge%20in%20cases%20of%20the%20Human%20Metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20was%20held%20under%20the%20chairmanship%20of%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Health%20Services%20(DGHS)%20in%20Delhi%20today%2C%20the%20government%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20from%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%2C%20Disaster%20Management%20Cell%2C%20Integrated%20Disease%20Surveillance%20Programme%20(IDSP)%2C%20National%20Centre%20for%20Disease%20Control%2C%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%2C%20Emergency%20Medical%20Relief%20Division%2C%20and%20hospitals%2C%20including%20AIIMS-Delhi%20participated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20monitoring%20group%20agreed%20that%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20present%20surge%20in%20China%20is%20the%20influenza%20virus%2C%20RSV%20and%20HMPV%20-%20the%20usual%20pathogens%20that%20are%20expected%20during%20the%20season%2C%20the%20government%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20government%20is%20keeping%20a%20close%20watch%20over%20the%20situation%20through%20all%20available%20channels%20and%20the%20WHO%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20share%20timely%20updates%20regarding%20the%20situation%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20robust%20surveillance%20system%20for%20influenza-like%20illness%20(ILI)%20and%20severe%20acute%20respiratory%20illness%20(SARI)%20for%20influenza%20is%20already%20in%20place%20in%20India%20through%20both%20the%20ICMR%20and%20IDSP%20networks%2C%20and%20data%20from%20both%20indicates%20no%20unusual%20surge%20in%20ILI%20and%20SARI%20cases%2C%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhysicians%20from%20hospitals%20confirmed%20there%20is%20no%20surge%20in%20respiratory%20illness%20cases%20in%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20other%20than%20the%20expected%20seasonal%20variation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICMR%20network%20also%20tests%20for%20other%20respiratory%20viruses%20such%20as%20adenovirus%2C%20RSV%2C%20HMPV%2C%20etc%20and%20these%20pathogens%20do%20not%20show%20an%20unusual%20increase%20in%20the%20tested%20samples%2C%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20precautionary%20measure%2C%20the%20ICMR%20will%20enhance%20the%20number%20of%20laboratories%20testing%20for%20HMPV%2C%20and%20will%20monitor%20trends%20of%20HMPV%20for%20the%20entire%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20from%20the%20recently%20conducted%20preparedness%20drill%20across%20the%20country%20indicated%20that%20India%20is%20well-prepared%20to%20deal%20with%20any%20increase%20in%20respiratory%20illnesses%2C%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20top%20official%20of%20the%20country's%20repository%20of%20technical%20knowledge%20on%20medical%20issues%20yesterday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-cause-for-alarm-indian-health-agency-on-hmpv-virus-spreading-in-china-7392255%5C%22%3Easked%20people%20not%20to%20panic%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20HMPV%20in%20China.%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Health%20Services%20(DGHS)%20official%20Dr%20Atul%20Goel%20suggested%20taking%20general%20precautions%20against%20all%20respiratory%20infections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20Otherwise%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20be%20alarmed%20about%20the%20present%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Goel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20specific%20antiviral%20treatment%20for%20HMPV%2C%20so%20prevention%20is%20key%20to%20controlling%20its%20spread%2C%20doctors%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20news%20doing%20the%20rounds%20about%20a%20Metapneumovirus%20outbreak%20in%20China.%20Let%20me%20be%20very%20clear%20on%20that%20count.%20Metapneumovirus%20is%20like%20any%20other%20respiratory%20virus%20which%20causes%20common%20cold%2C%20and%20in%20the%20very%20old%20and%20the%20very%20young%20it%20could%20cause%20flu-like%20symptoms%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Goel%20told%20reporters%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20analysed%20data%20of%20the%20respiratory%20outbreaks%20within%20the%20country.%20There%20is%20no%20substantial%20increase%20in%20December%202024%20data%20and%20no%20cases%20which%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20large%20numbers%20from%20any%20of%20our%20institutions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Goel%20said%20there%20is%20anyway%20an%20increased%20outbreak%20of%20respiratory%20virus%20infections%20in%20winter%2C%20for%20which%20hospitals%20are%20usually%20prepared%20with%20supplies%20and%20beds.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736005020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fg7ujpgsg_human-metapneumovirus-_625x300_03_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-unusual-surge-in-influenza-like-cases-says-india-amid-china-hmpv-spread-7400021%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20situation%20in%20China%20is%20not%20unusual%20in%20view%20of%20the%20ongoing%20flu%20season%2C%20a%20joint%20monitoring%20group%20has%20said%20amid%20reports%20of%20a%20surge%20in%20cases%20of%20the%20Human%20Metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MSME%20Pharma%20units%20get%20breather%20as%20govt%20extends%20Schedule%20M%20deadline%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736004932000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fmsme-pharma-units-get-breather-as-govt-extends-schedule-m-deadline-125010400719_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pharma%20cos%20with%20turnover%20of%20Rs%20250%20cr%20or%20less%20can%20submit%20an%20application%20to%20the%20central%20drugs%20regulator%20for%20one%20one-year%20extension%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findust