porting%20the%20company's%20stance%20on%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%20%E2%80%94%20a%20move%20that%20openly%20challenges%20the%20staying%20power%20of%20DEI%20critics%20ahead%20of%20a%20new%20presidential%20administration%20that%20has%20been%20critical%20of%20the%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20commitment%20to%20an%20enterprise%20rooted%20in%20respect%20and%20inclusion%20is%20appropriate%20and%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20board%20wrote%20last%20month%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-ceo-ron-vachris-salary-pay-package-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproxy%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20response%20to%20a%20shareholder%20proposal%20from%20the%20conservative%20National%20Center%20for%20Public%20Policy%20Research%2C%20which%20would%20have%20the%20company%20prepare%20a%20report%20on%20its%20DEI%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECostco's%20recommendation%20that%20shareholders%20vote%20against%20the%20proposal%20stands%20in%20contrast%20to%20several%20major%20companies%20opting%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-cutting-dei-activist-backlash-harley-davidson-deere-tractor-supply-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroll%20back%20their%20DEI%20initiatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20past%20year%20and%20a%20half%20amid%20a%20slate%20of%20lawsuits%20and%20shareholder%20proposals.%20Some%20companies%20have%20also%20taken%20to%20referencing%20DEI%20policies%20as%20a%20risk%20factor%20in%20their%20financial%20filings%2C%20pointing%20to%20potential%20legal%20action%20or%20reputational%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Costco%20appears%20to%20be%20bucking%20the%20anti-DEI%20wave%20by%20defending%20its%20diversity%20initiatives%2C%20data%20suggests%20shareholders%20largely%20support%20diversity%20efforts%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20backlash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.conference-board.org%2Fpublications%2F2024-proxy-season-review-corporate-resilience-in-a-polarized-landscape%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Conference%20Board%20indicated%20that%20while%20the%20volume%20of%20shareholder%20proposals%20targeting%20diversity%20and%20equity%20more%20than%20tripled%20year-over-year%20during%20the%20January%20to%20June%20proxy%20season%20in%202024%2C%20actual%20support%20for%20anti-ESG%20proposals%20has%20fallen%20from%205%25%20to%202%25%20during%20the%20same%20period.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20tripling%20of%20proposals%20might%20seem%20large%2C%20the%20actual%20numbers%20are%20relatively%20small%3A%20five%20such%20shareholder%20proposals%20in%202023%20and%2017%20in%202024%20out%20of%20the%C2%A03%2C000%20publicly%20traded%20firms%20that%20represent%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20US%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20public%20companies%20in%20the%20US%20saw%20shareholder%20proposals%20on%20DEI%20matters%2C%20with%20anti-DEI%20proposals%20receiving%20less%20than%202%25%20support%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study.%20By%20comparison%2C%20proposals%20on%20social%20issues%20that%20weren't%20backed%20by%20anti-ESG%20groups%20saw%20roughly%2020%25%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECostco's%20move%20could%20flip%20the%20script%20on%20the%20perceived%20popularity%20of%20anti-DEI%20proposals%20and%20requests%20to%20look%20into%20the%20matter%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20the%20proponent's%20request%20for%20a%20study%20reflects%20a%20policy%20bias%20with%20which%20we%20disagree%20and%20that%20further%20study%20and%20reporting%20would%20not%20be%20an%20efficient%20use%20of%20Company%20resources%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20famously%20frugal%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELA%20Times%20columnist%20Michael%20Hiltzik%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20companies'%20inconsistent%20positions%20on%20social%20and%20political%20issues%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lat