20Among%203%20Arrested%20For%20Journalist%20Mukesh%20Chandrakar's%20Murder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThree%20people%2C%20including%20two%20relatives%2C%20have%20been%20arrested%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20journalist%20Mukesh%20Chandrakar%2C%20whose%20body%20was%20found%20in%20a%20septic%20tank%20in%20a%20shed%20owned%20by%20a%20contractor%20in%20Chattisgarh's%20Bastar%20division%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrakar%2C%20an%20independent%20journalist%20who%20was%20also%20a%20contributing%20reporter%20for%20NDTV%2C%20was%20last%20seen%20leaving%20his%20home%20in%20Bijapur's%20Pujari%20Para%20on%20New%20Year's%20Day%20and%20his%20brother%2C%20Yukesh%2C%20had%20filed%20a%20missing%20complaint%20the%20next%20day.%20After%20beginning%20an%20investigation%2C%20police%20found%20the%2032-year-old's%20body%20in%20Chhatan%20Para%20Basti%2C%20not%20very%20far%20from%20his%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERitesh%20Chandrakar%2C%20Mukesh's%20cousin%2C%20was%20arrested%20from%20Raipur%20airport%20on%20Saturday%20while%20Mahendra%20Ramteke%2C%20a%20supervisor%2C%20and%20Dinesh%20Chandrakar%2C%20another%20relative%20of%20Mukesh%2C%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%20from%20Bijapur.%20Contractor%20Suresh%20Chandrakar%2C%20the%20alleged%20mastermind%20behind%20the%20murder%2C%20is%20on%20the%20run.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpur%20Of%20The%20Moment%20Or%20Pre-Planned%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20Chandrakar%20had%20dinner%20with%20his%20cousin%20Ritesh%20and%20Mahendra%20Ramteke%20in%20Suresh's%20shed%20and%20an%20argument%20broke%20out%20between%20them.%20Ritesh%20and%20Mahendra%20allegedly%20attacked%20Chandrakar%20with%20an%20iron%20rod%2C%20killing%20him%20on%20the%20spot%2C%20and%20then%20hid%20his%20body%20in%20a%20septic%20tank%2C%20sealing%20it%20with%20cement%20to%20conceal%20the%20crime.%20They%20also%20disposed%20of%20Mukesh's%20phone%20and%20the%20weapon%20used%20in%20the%20murder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDinesh%2C%20the%20other