emphasised%20that%20he%20had%20recently%20%26quot%3Breported%20on%20an%20alleged%20road%20construction%20scam%20that%20prompted%20local%20authorities%20to%20investigate%20some%20contractors%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20young%20journalist's%20death%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20grave%20concern%20as%20it%20raises%20suspicion%20of%20foul%20play.%20The%20Editors%20Guild%20calls%20on%20the%20government%20of%20Chhattisgarh%20to%20spare%20no%20efforts%20in%20investigating%20the%20case%20speedily%20and%20bringing%20the%20guilty%20to%20book.%20The%20safety%20of%20journalists%20-%20especially%20those%20working%20in%20smaller%20towns%20and%20rural%20areas%20-%20is%20of%20paramount%20importance%2C%20and%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20demands%20that%20authorities%20across%20the%20country%20must%20do%20their%20best%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20harm%20or%20hindrance%20is%20caused%20to%20any%20of%20them%20in%20discharging%20their%20professional%20duties%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Guild%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736003520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Ftb481avg_mukesh-chandrakar_625x300_03_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchhattisgarh-journalist-murder-contractor-2-relatives-among-3-arrested-for-journalist-mukesh-chandrakars-murder-7399934%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20people%2C%20including%20two%20relatives%2C%20have%20been%20arrested%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20journalist%20Mukesh%20Chandrakar%2C%20who%20had%20been%20missing%20since%20Wednesday%20and%20whose%20body%20was%20found%20in%20a%20septic%20tank%20in%20a%20shed%20owned%20by%20a%20contractor%20in%20Chattisgarh's%20Bastar%20division.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arjun%20blames%20Varun%20for%20less%20work%20with%20KJo%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A17360026180