C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubhash's%20wife%20Nikita%20Singhania%2C%20her%20mother%20Nisha%20Singhania%20and%20brother%20Anurag%20Singhania%20had%20approached%20the%20session%20court%20in%20Bengaluru%20for%20bail%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20earlier%20appealed%20to%20the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20to%20direct%20the%20session%20court%20to%20dispose%20of%20their%20bail%20Petition.%20The%20High%20Court%20directed%20the%20session%20court%20to%20dispose%20of%20the%20petition%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2014%2C%C2%A0Nikita%20Singhania%20was%20arrested%20from%20Gurugram%20while%20her%20mother%20and%20brother%20Anurag%20were%20picked%20up%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Prayagraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2034-year-old%20had%20left%20behind%20a%20video%20and%2024-page%20note%20detailing%20his%20marital%20issues%2C%20harassment%20and%20attempts%20of%20extortion%20by%20his%20estranged%20wife%2C%20her%20relatives%20and%20an%20Uttar%20Pradesh-based%20judge.%20He%20accused%20his%20wife%20and%20her%20relatives%20of%20driving%20him%20to%20suicide%20through%20%26quot%3Bfalse%26quot%3B%20cases%20and%20%26quot%3Bpersistent%20torture%26quot%3B.%20He%20had%20also%20accused%20his%20wife%20of%20demanding%20Rs%203%20crore%20to%20settle%20the%20case%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubhash%20and%20Singhania%20got%20married%20in%202019.%20They%20had%20a%20son%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20of%20the%20techie%20have%20sought%20the%20custody%20of%20their%20four-year-old%20grandson%2C%20claiming%20they%20do%20not%20know%20his%20whereabouts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20son%20was%20broken%20from%20inside...%20Even%20after%20torture%20by%20his%20wife%20and%20in-laws%2C%20he%20didn't%20tell%20anyone%20about%20it.%20His%20suicide%20note%20also%20mentioned%20that%20his%20parents%20be%20given%20custody%20of%20his%20child%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Pawan%20Kumar%2C%20the%20father%20of%20Subhash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20waiting%20for%20the%20January%207%20hearing%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20this%20regard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20claimed%20that%20Ms%20Singhania%20treated%20her%20son%20as%20an%20%26quot%3BATM%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%26quot%3BMy%20grandson%20was%20ATM%20to%20her.%20She%20got%20money%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20taking%20care%20of%20him.%20She%20approached%20the%20High%20Court%20demanding%20Rs%2020%2C000%20to%20Rs%2040%2C000.%20She%20went%20on%20to%20appeal%20for%20Rs%2080%2C000.%20Even%20after%20this%2C%20she%20went%20on%20demanding%20more%20money.%20Hence%2C%20we%20have%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20child%20as%20he%20is%20safe%20with%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20counsel%20for%20Atul%20Subhash%20had%20argued%20that%20the%20accused%20wife%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20use%20the%20child%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20get%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20stand%20was%20that%20the%20crime%2C%20which%20they%20have%20committed%20is%20very%20heinous%2C%20additionally%20we%20have%20filed%20a%20habeas%20corpus%20petition%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20where%20the%20court%20has%20passed%20directions%20to%20the%20three%20states%20UP%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Haryana%20for%20ascertaining%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20the%20kid%20and%20once%20the%20child%20is%20found%2C%20accordingly%20will%20pass%20directions%20for%20considering%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20kid%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20techie's%20lawyer%20Akash%20Jindal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736000940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fso3tati_atul-subhash-nikita-singhania_625x300_15_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwife-her-mother-and-brother-get-bail-in-case-of-abetting-bengaluru-techie-atul-subhashs-suicide-7399133%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wife%2C%20her%20mother%20and%20brother%20get%20bail%20in%20case%20of%20abetting%20Bengaluru%20techie%20