the%20protests%2C%20demanding%20a%20re-examination%20and%20compensation%20for%20the%20family%20of%20a%20BPSC%20aspirant%20who%20allegedly%20died%20by%20suicide.%20Prominent%20figures%2C%20such%20as%20Prashant%20Kishor%2C%20founder%20of%20Jansuraj%2C%20are%20currently%20on%20an%20indefinite%20strike%2C%20while%20Independent%20MP%20from%20Purnea%2C%20Pappu%20Yadav%2C%20led%20a%20rail%20roko%20protest%20on%20January%203%20in%20support%20of%20the%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20intensified%20after%20shocking%20CCTV%20footage%20from%20a%20BPSC%20exam%20centre%20surfaced%2C%20showing%20candidates%20tearing%20question%20papers%20and%20snatching%20them%20from%20fellow%20test-takers.%20The%20footage%20reveals%20candidates%20rushing%20into%20a%20room%20where%20exam%20officials%20were%20addressing%20concerns%20about%20a%2040-45%20minute%20delay%20in%20distributing%20the%20question%20papers.%20Despite%20reassurances%20that%20lost%20time%20would%20be%20compensated%2C%20some%20candidates%20caused%20a%20disturbance%2C%20pushing%20officials%20aside%20and%20raiding%20boxes%20containing%20question%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authorities%20explained%20in%20a%20police%20complaint%20that%20the%20sealed%20question%20paper%20boxes%20were%20opened%20properly%2C%20but%20the%20delay%20led%20to%20unrest.%20%26quot%3BCandidates%20demanded%20explanations%20for%20the%20delay%20and%2C%20upon%20hearing%20the%20noise%2C%20others%20joined%20in%2C%20creating%20chaos%20and%20tearing%20question%20papers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736000340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fl72oaq5g_bpsc-70th-prelims-reexam-2024_625x300_04_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fbpsc-70th-prelims-re-exam-2024-5-943-out-of-12-012-students-appear-amid-protests-7399630%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BPSC%2070th%20Prelims%20Re-Exam%202024%3A%20The%20re-exam%20was%20held%20at%202