parliament%20in%20london%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67742d61ca1058716a5ee202%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20lived%20in%20both%20New%20York%20City%20and%20London.%3Cp%3EAlexander%20Spatari%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20a%20lawyer%2C%20I%20got%20the%20chance%20to%20live%20in%20both%20New%20York%20City%20and%20London.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20found%20New%20York%20City%20to%20be%20full%20of%20life%2C%20but%20it%20was%20too%20expensive%20and%20party-focused.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELondon%20was%20cheaper%2C%20and%20I%20could%20picture%20a%20future%20there.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can%20remember%2C%20I've%20always%20had%20two%20cities%20in%20mind%20when%20I%20thought%20about%20the%20most%20bustling%20business%20hubs%20in%20the%20world%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-nyc-to-london-better-work-life-balance-healthcare-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20City%20and%20London%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20mind%2C%20it%20never%20got%20any%20better%20than%20the%20Big%20Apple%20or%20the%20British%20capital.%20They%20were%20the%20cities%20to%20make%20it%20in%20the%20arts%20or%20the%20corporate%20world.%20From%20Broadway%20and%20the%20West%20End%20to%20Canary%20Wharf%20and%20Wall%20Street%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20experience%20it%20all.%20My%20dream%20was%20to%20live%20in%20one%20of%20them%20at%20some%20point%20in%20life%20to%20try%20my%20luck%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcorporate-laywer-quit-big-law-morals-pay-cut-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecorporate%20lawyer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHard%20work%2C%20perseverance%2C%20and%20a%20bit%20of%20luck%20gave%20me%20the%20opportunity%20to%20live%20in%20both%20of%20them.%20Both%20are%20chaotically%20enchanting%2C%20absurdly%20overpriced%2C%20and%20fast-paced%2C%20but%20if%20I%20had%20to%20pick%20one%20to%20live%20in%20today%2C%20it%20would%20be%20London.%20Here's%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dbfd3f67-1e0d-4267-8e2e-e2c80da82cb6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20couldn't%20picture%20my%20life%20long-term%20in%20New%20York%20City%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20first%20lived%20in%20New%20York%20City%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20center%20of%20Manhattan%2C%20to%20be%20precise.%20I%20moved%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Factivities-tourists-cant-miss-in-mexico-city-cdmx-local-tips-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMexico%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20end%20of%202020%20and%20stayed%20there%20for%20a%20year.%20Yes%2C%20it%20was%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20pandemic.%20But%20my%20experience%20of%20the%20city%20wasn't%20affected%20negatively%20by%20that.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20I%20got%20to%20see%20an%20empty%20New%20York%20go%20from%20zero%20to%20100%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20months.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20better%20and%20for%20worse%2C%20the%20city%20was%20everything%20that%20I%20expected%3A%20dirty%2C%20cosmopolitan%2C%20full%20of%20concrete%2C%20and%20way%20too%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20beyond%20the%20unrealistic%20price%20tags%20and%20tall%20skyscrapers%2C%20I%20also%20got%20to%20appreciate%20the%20city's%20%3Cspan%3Eunique%20attributes%3A%20its%20social%20aspect%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-restaurants-in-nyc-places-to-eat-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eiconic%20restaurants%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20unmatchable%20style%2C%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Ecolorful%20neighborhoods.%20The%20city%20is%20full%20of%20life.%20In%20every%20corner%20of%20every%20street%2C%20I%20could%20feel%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20those%20attributes%20that%20made%20it%20so%20desirable%20for%20a%20short%20stay%20were%20exactly%20what%20made%20New%20York%20City%20a%20clear%20%26quot%3Bno%26quot%3B%20for%20my%20long-term%20plans.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyc-to-florida-near-disney-world-best-worst-parts-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20ethereal%20and%20unapologetic.%20Yes%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20life-changing.%20But%20I%20couldn't%20see%20myself%20partying%20and%20working%2024%2F7%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cd82a279-b836-4bc0-b704-3c59bf561944%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELife%20in%20London%20seemed%20more%20manageable%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20to%20London%20at%20the%20end%20of%202021%20%E2%80%94%20after%20both%20Brexit%20and%20the%20pandemic.%20Both%20the%20city%20and%20I%20felt%20like%20we%20needed%20a%20fresh%20start.%20So%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-traveling-to-london-england%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscover%20London%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20comparative%20perspective.%20I%20analyzed%20every%20one%20of%20its%20major%20aspects%20against%20those%20of%20its%20American%20counterpart.%20The%20results%20were%20surprising%20as%20I%20found%20similarities%20between%20them%20where%20I%20thought%20there%20would%20be%20clear%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20starters%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20London%20was%20famous%20for%20its%20dreary%20and%20often%20gray%20weather%2C%20but%20when%20I%20moved%20there%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20it%20wasn't%20as%20bad%20as%20I%20thought%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20compared%20to%20the%20extreme%20heat%20or%20cold%20of%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20thought%20London%20would%20be%20more%20expensive.%20However%2C%20I%20found%20that%20rent%20and%20travel%20were%20much%20more%20affordable%20and%20diverse%20than%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupercommuting-nyc-dc-helps-career-development-salary-millennial-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Apple%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELondon%20suddenly%20(without%20even%20considering%20its%20majestic%20history%20and%20stunning%20beauty)%20became%20a%20place%20I%20could%20call%20home%20for%20a%20longer%20period%20of%20time.%20I%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20busy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-today-jackson-hole-wyoming-america-billionaire-hub%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20hub%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20more%20things%20than%20just%20work%20or%20parties.%20There%20were%20parks%2C%20museums%2C%20schools%2C%20recreational%20areas%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224860e74f-bf58-47c0-9dde-de4bb209be49%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELondon%20felt%20more%20mature%20and%20like%20home%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20New%20York%20City%20reminds%20me%20of%20my%20most%20toxic%20ex%3A%20the%20intensity%2C%20the%20beauty%2C%20and%20the%20danger.%20Just%20like%20with%20my%20ex%2C%20I%20knew%20it%20wouldn't%20last%20long%2C%20and%20that's%20what%20made%20it%20so%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20London%20reminds%20me%20of%20my%20most%20stable%20relationship%3A%20its%20pragmatism%2C%20its%20elegance%2C%20its%20maturity%2C%20and%20its%20sense%20of%20purpose.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20could%20build%20my%20life%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20City%20should%20be%20your%20sole%20option%20if%20you%20are%20young%20and%20ambitious.%20But%20be%20sure%20to%20move%20to%20London%20when%20you%20want%20to%20grow%20old%20and%20have%20a%20family%20before%20it's%20too%20late.%20That's%20just%20what%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-city-london-lived-both-cities-prefer-british-capital-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735999621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67742d61ca105