Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20if%20Indian%20scores%20more%2040%20runs%20or%20they%20put%20185%20on%20the%20board%20then%20they%20have%20a%20great%20chance%20but%20it%20all%20depends%20on%20Jasprit%20Bumrah's%20fitness.%20If%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20is%20fit%20then%20145-150%20might%20be%20enough.%20But%20if%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20is%20not%20fit%20then%20a%20score%20of%20around%20200%20also%20might%20not%20be%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20told%20Star%20Sports%20during%20an%20interaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGavaskar%20went%20on%20to%20add%20that%20India's%20decision%20to%20maintain%20secrecy%20over%20Bumrah's%20availability%20was%20the%20right%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20that%20I%20liked%20was%20when%20he%20came%20back%20after%20the%20scan%2C%20obviously%20it%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20because%20the%20hospital%20is%20a%20bit%20far%2C%20but%20he%20looked%20in%20good%20shape%20and%20his%20body%20language%20was%20such%20that%20there%20was%20no%20indication%20of%20the%20Australian%20team%20and%20it%20is%20very%20important%20to%20maintain%20the%20secrecy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%2C%20tactically%20you%20do%20not%20want%20to%20announce%20whether%20Bumrah%20will%20be%20available%20for%20bowling%20or%20not%2C%20and%20even%20if%20he%20is%20not%20available%20and%20this%20news%20goes%20across%20the%20opposition%20dressing%20room%20because%20till%20now%20Australian%20batsmen%20haven't%20found%20out%20a%20way%20to%20counter%20him%2C%20they%20don't%20know%20whether%20they%20should%20attack%2C%20defend%2C%20or%20whether%20they%20should%20play%20on%20front-foot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20to%20execute%20this%20plan%20it%20is%20important%20to%20maintain%20secrecy%2C%20so%20Bumrah%20and%20the%20Indian%20team%20management%20managed%20it%20quite%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20IANS%20Inputs)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735998600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fhetnkfng_bumrah-afp_625x300_30_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fjasprit-bumrah-less-india-given-reality-check-by-sunil-gavaskar-might-not-be-enough-7399270%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20a%20total%20of%2015%20wickets%20fell%20on%20Day%202%2C%20India%20stand-in%20Jasprit%20Bumrah's%20injury%20was%20the%20highlight%20of%20the%20day.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fjasprit-bumrah-less-india-given-reality-check-by-sunil-gavaskar-might-not-be-enough-7399270%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20A%20First%2C%20Life%20Sprouts%20On%20ISRO's%20Space%20Lab%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20first%20for%20India%2C%20life%20has%20sprouted%20on%20a%20craft%20sent%20into%20space%20by%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECowpea%20seeds%20sent%20on%20the%20PS4-Orbital%20Experiment%20Module%20(POEM)%2C%20or%20the%20Bharatiya%20Space%20Lab%2C%20have%20germinated%20in%20the%20near%20zero-gravity%20and%20enclosed%20surroundings%20of%20space%20-%20and%20leaves%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20grow%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20experiment%20was%20part%20of%20the%20SpaDeX%20or%20space%20docking%20experiment%20launched%20on%20December%2030%2C%202024%2C%20using%20the%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(PSLV).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20the%20ISRO%20handle%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BLife%20sprouts%20in%20space!%20VSSC's%20CROPS%20(Compact%20Research%20Module%20for%20Orbital%20Plant%20Studies)%20experiment%20onboard%20PSLV-C60%20POEM-4%20successfully%20sprouted%20cowpea%20seeds%20in%204%20days.%20Leaves%20expected%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20Chairman%20Dr%20S%20Somanath%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20successful%20experiment%20could%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20human%20space%20mission%20(Gaganyaan)%20and%20the%20plan%20to%20build%20an%20Indian%20space%20station%20(Bharatiya%20Antariksha%20Station).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20exciting%20to%20see%20life%20sprouting%20on%20the%20Bharatiya%20Space%20Lab.%20This%20cowpea%20germination%20test%20is%20the%20maiden%20attempt%20to%20try%20and%20understand%2C%20through%20our%20own%20experiments%2C%20how%20life%20works%20in%20space.%20It%20also%20gives%20confidence%20in%20the%20environment%20control%20and%20life%20support%20system%20(ECLSS)%20deployed%20on%20board%20the%20Indian%20orbital%20module%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Somanath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20one%20small%20step%20for%20POEM%20may%20help%20write%20a%20whole%20new%20novel%20on%20life%20support%20for%20Gaganyaan%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Antariksha%20Station...%20a%20big%20learning%20for%20India%20from%20a%20small%20experiment%2C%20since%20no%20one%20shares%20these%20seemingly%20simple%20but%20challenging%20bits%20of%20complex%20life-support%20technologies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EObjective%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20in-house%20team%20of%20ISRO's%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20Space%20Centre%20(VSSC)%2C%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20the%20objective%20was%20to%20demonstrate%20how%20cowpea%20seeds%20germinate%20in%20the%20near-zero-gravity%20environment%20of%20space.%20What%20made%20the%20experiment%20challenging%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20seedlings%20lose%20orientation%20when%20grown%20in%20microgravity%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStudying%20plant%20growth%20in%20space%20is%20new%20to%20ISRO%20and%20the%2015-member%20team%20is%20very%20excited%20to%20see%20the%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20T%20Latha%2C%20VSSC%20Deputy%20Director%2C%20who%20is%20heading%20the%20experiment.%20She%20says%20cowpea%20(Vigna%20unguiculata%2C%20known%20as%20'lobia'%20in%20Hindi)%20was%20chosen%20as%20its%20seeds%20can%20germinate%20and%20grow%20leaves%20in%20less%20than%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20POEM%20module%20is%20also%20carrying%20two%20other%20live%20biology%20experiments%20that%20will%20attempt%20to%20grow%20gut%20bacteria%20and%20spinach%20cells.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735998300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fsbum6pjg_isro-cowpea-seed-experiment_625x300_04_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fspadex-poem-india-in-space-cowpea-in-a-first-life-sprouts-on-isros-space-lab-7399316%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20first%20for%20India%2C%20life%20has%20sprouted%20on%20a%20craft%20sent%20into%20space%20by%20the%20country.%20Cowpea%20seeds%20sent%20on%20the%20PS4-Orbital%20Experiment%20Module%20(POEM)%20or%20the%20Bharatiya%20Space%20Labhave%20germinated%20in%20the%20near%20zero-gravity%20and%20enclosed%20surroundings%20of%20space.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fspadex-poem-india-in-space-cowpea-in-a-first-life-sprouts-on-isros-space-lab-7399316%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indra%20reveals%20Madhuri%20was%20once%20called%20B'wood's%20jinxed%20girl%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735998220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116944871%2Cimgsize-45914.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Findra-kumar-reveals-madhuri-dixit-was-once-called-bollywoods-jinxed-girl-when-i-signed-her-for-beta-everyone-said-paagal-hogaya-hai-tu%2Farticleshow%2F116944892.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116944892.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMadhuri%20Dixit%20is%20celebrated%20as%20one%20of%20Bollywood's%20biggest%20superstars%2C%20but%20her%20journey%20to%20fame%20was%20not%20without%20struggles.%20In%20a%20conv