s%20can%20be%20tricky.%20Many%20renters%20struggle%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20make%20an%20apartment%20feel%20like%20home%20without%20doing%20major%20renovations%20and%20potentially%20violating%20the%20terms%20of%20their%20lease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20Business%20Insider%20asked%20interior%20designers%20for%20tips%20on%20making%20a%20rental%20feel%20more%20luxurious%20without%20making%20big%20changes.%20Here's%20what%20they%20had%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EChoosing%20a%20focal%20point%20to%20decorate%20around%20can%20make%20a%20room%20feel%20more%20elegant.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223509%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20living%20room%20with%20a%20tall%20wooden%20roof%2C%20large%20abstract%20painting%20behind%20a%20white%20couch%2C%20two%20blue%20chairs%2C%20and%20a%20two%20coffee%20tables.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67290e53192f52589855e607%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222632%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDesigning%20a%20room%20symmetrically%20helps%20to%20add%20unity%20to%20a%20space.%3Cp%3EAndreas%20von%20Einsiedel%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDecorating%20around%20a%20specific%20element%2C%20like%20a%20fireplace%20or%20a%20piece%20of%20wall%20art%2C%20can%20bring%20symmetry%20and%20unity%20to%20a%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20interior%20designer%20Tommy%20Kebbson%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tommykebbson.co.uk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKebbson%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20can%20instantly%20make%20a%20space%20feel%20more%20elegant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20small%20adjustments%20like%20placing%20lamps%20on%20either%20side%20of%20a%20sofa%20or%20balancing%20artwork%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20a%20wall%20can%20make%20a%20significant%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKebbson%20also%20told%20BI%20that%20a%20symmetrical%20space%20doesn't%20mean%20all%20elements%20have%20to%20be%20identic