%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20used%20to%20bounce%20back%20quickly%20after%20a%20long%20day%20of%20work%20and%20chasing%20toddlers.%20At%2040%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20I%20needed%20a%20recovery%20plan%20just%20to%20survive%20a%20trip%20to%20the%20grocery%20store.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fwhen-do-you-start-showing-in-pregnancy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20baby%20bump%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20wasn't%20as%20perky%20as%20it%20used%20to%20be%2C%20and%20my%20back%20wasn't%20as%20forgiving%20when%20I%20bent%20over%20to%20tie%20my%20shoes.%20Every%20movement%20felt%20like%20a%20yoga%20class%20I%20hadn't%20signed%20up%20for.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20doctor's%20appointments%20also%20took%20a%20bit%20more%20effort.%20Not%20just%20the%20regular%20ones%20%E2%80%94%20I%20had%20extra%20blood%20tests%2C%20ultrasounds%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Badvanced%20maternal%20age%26quot%3B%20reminders.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20days%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20moving%20at%20a%20toddler's%20pace%20just%20to%20keep%20up.%20My%20knees%20and%20ankles%20creak.%20My%20energy%20levels%20are%20more%20in%20line%20with%20someone%20preparing%20for%20a%20nap%20than%20chasing%20after%20a%20baby%20%E2%80%94%20the%20only%20thing%20I%20asked%20Santa%20for%20Christmas%20was%20uninterrupted%20sleep.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20can't%20tell%20you%20how%20often%20I've%20looked%20at%20my%20husband%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20too%20old%20for%20this!%26quot%3B%20And%20yet%2C%20when%20that%20baby%20smiles%20at%20me%20when%20I%20hear%20that%20little%20giggle%2C%20I%20remember%20exactly%20why%20I'm%20doing%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20biggest%20challenge%20isn't%20just%20physical%2C%20though.%20I%20remember%20juggling%20a%20newborn%20with%20work%20and%20life%20in%20my%2020s%2C%20thinking%20I%20was%20some%20kind%20of%20superwoman