%20with%20their%20carefully%20crafted%20misinformation%20campaigns%20aimed%20at%20creating%20fear%20and%20panic%20among%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20office-bearers%20and%20leadership%20of%20the%20Catholic%20Bishops'%20Conference%20of%20India%20(CBCI)%20have%20become%20the%20latest%20targets%20of%20criticism-first%2C%20for%20inviting%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20who%20has%20long%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20their%20vilification%20campaigns%2C%20and%20second%2C%20for%20their%20alleged%20silence%20on%20issues%20with%20clear%20political%20undertones.%20Expecting%20the%20bishop's%20body%20to%20invite%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20conditionally%20or%20to%20raise%20specific%20issues%20during%20the%20event%20reflects%20a%20limited%20perspective.%20Christmas%20is%20a%20celebration%20that%20transcends%20political%20agendas%20and%20is%20marked%20by%20unity%20and%20goodwill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fqbjs0lo8_narendra-modi-reuters_625x300_01_January_25.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20taking%20office%20in%202014%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20consistently%20promoted%20the%20mantra%20of%20%26quot%3BSabka%20Saath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas%2C%20Sabka%20Vishwas%2C%20Sabka%20Prayas%2C%26quot%3B%20aiming%20to%20foster%20development%20and%20unity%20for%20all%20Indians.%20Nowhere%20is%20this%20vision%20more%20visible%20than%20in%20India's%20northeastern%20region%2C%20where%20the%20Modi's%20government%20launched%20the%20%26quot%3BAct%20East%26quot%3B%20policy%20to%20bring%20transformative%20changes%20in%20infrastructure%2C%20connectivity%2C%20and%20capacity%20development.%20The%20government's%20efforts%20have%20resulted%20in%20over%20Rs%205%20lakh%20crore%20in%20investments%2C%20with%20noticeable%20improvements%20in%20various%20sectors.%20The%20northeast%20is%20home%20to%20a%20large%20Christian%20population%2C%20with%20states%20like%20Nagaland%2C%20Mizoram%2C%20and%20Meghalaya%20having%20Christian%20majorities.%20Seven%20out%20of%20the%20eight%20states%20in%20the%20region%20are%20currently%20governed%20by%20the%20NDA%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20securing%20electoral%20wins%20in%20areas%20where%20national%20minorities%2C%20including%20Christians%20and%20Buddhists%2C%20form%20the%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20has%20made%20significant%20strides%20in%20curbing%20insurgency%20movements%20across%20the%20northeast%2C%20some%20of%20which%20persisted%20until%20the%20early%202010s.%20By%20prioritising%20peace%20through%20dialogue%20and%20consensus%2C%20the%20government%20has%20helped%20bring%20stability%20to%20a%20region%20long%20plagued%20by%20unrest.%20Yet%2C%20in%20Manipur%2C%20where%20an%20age-old%20ethnic%20conflict%20is%20mischievously%20framed%20as%20religious%20strife%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20faces%20unwarranted%20criticism%20from%20some%20quarters.%20In%202023%2C%20while%20this%20conflict%20was%20at%20its%20peak%2C%20the%20senior-most%20Cardinal%20in%20India%2C%20Gracias%20Oswald%2C%20an%20advisor%20of%20Pope%20Francis%20had%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20these%20lines%2C%20with%20an%20appeal%20to%20not%20do%20anything%20that%20would%20worsen%20the%20situation%20between%20two%20tribes%20historically%20hostile%20to%20each%20other.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20in%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20house%20stated%20clearly%20the%20efforts%20made%20to%20restore%20peace%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F3qvo880g_bjp-generic-with-modi_625x300_08_September_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20criticism%20of%20the%20Modi%20government's%20handling%20of%20the%20Waqf%20Bill%20reflects%20a%20degree%20of%20hypocrisy%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20overt%20involvement%20of%20Opposition%20MPs%2C%20as%20highlighted%20by%20Derek%20O'Brien%20in%20a%20recent%20op-ed%20in%20The%20Indian%20Express.%20These%20MPs%20reportedly%20sought%20to%20pressure%20the%20bishops'%20body%20into%20adopting%20a%20stance%20contrary%20to%20the%20broader%20interests%20of%20the%20Christian%20community.%20The%20Waqf%20Bill%20controversy%20underscores%20ongoing%20tensions%20in%20Kerala%2C%20where%20the%20church%20has%20voiced%20concerns%20over%20the%20state's%20Waqf%20Board%20claiming%20404%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20predominantly%20belonging%20to%20Latin%20Catholic%20families.%20The%20BJP%20has%20expressed%20solidarity%20with%20the%20church%2C%20supporting%20its%20stance%20on%20safeguarding%20constitutionally%20guaranteed%20property%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20amended%20the%20Foreign%20Contribution%20Regulation%20Act%20(FCRA)%20in%202020%20to%20ensure%20greater%20transparency%20in%20the%20use%20of%20foreign%20funds%20by%20non-governmental%20organizations%20(NGOs).%20This%20move%20led%20to%20the%20cancellation%20of%20more%20than%2019%2C000%20NGO%20registrations%20for%20misusing%20funds%20between%202011%20and%202019.%20In%202023%2C%2026%20new%20FCRA%20registrations%20were%20granted%20for%20Christian%20programmes%2C%20and%2027%20for%20Hindu%20initiatives.%20However%2C%20the%20Opposition%20persists%20in%20misrepresenting%20the%20government's%20actions%20as%20being%20anti-Christian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F1o0kn8n8_prime-minister-narendra-modi_625x300_26_December_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20over%20religious%20conversions%20has%20been%20a%20constant%20point%20of%20contention.%20The%20Modi%20government%20supports%20laws%20passed%20by%20various%20states%20to%20prevent%20forced%20conversions%2C%20emphasising%20that%20individuals%20must%20have%20the%20right%20to%20convert%20only%20voluntarily.%20These%20laws%20are%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20guarantees%20freedom%20of%20religion%20but%20does%20not%20permit%20coercion%20in%20conversion%20practices.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20affirmed%20the%20right%20to%20convert%2C%20as%20long%20as%20the%20conversion%20is%20genuine%20and%20voluntary.%20These%20measures%20are%20intended%20to%20protect%20vulnerable%20groups%2C%20particularly%20socio-linguistic%20minorities%2C%20SCs%2C%20and%20STs%2C%20whose%20rights%20and%20customs%20are%20protected%20by%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20repeated%20barbs%20on%20the%20celebration%20of%20Good%20Governance%20Day.%20It%20is%20not%20to%20be%20forgotten%20that%20December%2025th%20is%20the%20Birth%20anniversary%20of%20BJP's%20founding%20president%20and%20the%20party's%20first%20ever%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee.%20The%20week%20from%2019%20to%2025%20of%20December%20is%20celebrated%20as%20good%20governance%20week%20to%20honour%20Vajpayee's%20contribution%20towards%20nation-building.%20Participation%20in%20this%20is%20voluntary.%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20along%20with%20party%20workers%2C%20join%20India's%20Christians%20in%20celebrating%20Christmas%20on%20the%20same%20day.%20National%20leaders%20like%20PM%20Modi%20and%20BJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20have%20set%20visible%20examples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20BJP's%20political%20detractors%20may%20question%20the%20stances%20of%20the%20government%20and%20the%20church%20leadership%20on%20issues%20affecting%20the%20Christian%20community%2C%20such%20criticisms%20largely%20stem%20from%20their%20exasperation%20at%20failing%20to%20distance%20minorities%20from%20the%20BJP.%20The%20trust%20placed%20in%20PM%20Modi's%20leadership%20and%20actions%20by%20a%20diverse%20cross-section%20of%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20inclu