acks%20and%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20failed%20Delhi%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20lacking%20a%20chief%20ministerial%20face%20and%20substantive%20issues%20ahead%20of%20the%20upcoming%20Delhi%20Assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%2010%20years%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20not%20done%20a%20single%20significant%20thing%20in%20Delhi.%20They%20promised%20permanent%20housing%20by%202022%20but%20have%20built%20only%204%2C700%20houses%20in%20five%20years.%20Compare%20that%20to%20AAP's%20work%3A%2022%2C000%20classrooms%2C%20three%20new%20universities%2C%20and%20countless%20developmental%20initiatives%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20today%20released%20its%20first%20list%20for%20the%20Delhi%20Assembly%20elections.%20Parvesh%20Verma%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20the%20New%20Delhi%20constituency%20to%20take%20on%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20while%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20will%20contest%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20for%20the%20Kalkaji%20constituency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735984260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fsv84fp7g_amit-shah-arvind-kejriwal-_625x300_04_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-elections-2025-after-pm-modi-amit-shahs-sheeshmahal-attack-on-arvind-kejriwal-7398072%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20today%20followed%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20target%20AAP%20chief%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20for%20his%20allegedly%20extravagant%20expenditure%20on%20the%20official%20residence%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Delhi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-elections-2025-after-pm-modi-amit-shahs-sheeshmahal-attack-on-arvind-kejriwal-7398072%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World's%20oldest%20livin