neswar%20to%20the%20facility%20every%20morning%20to%20oversee%20daily%20operations.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20CCTV%20camera%2C%20but%20the%20team%20still%20needs%20guidance%20and%20monitoring.%20I%20also%20meet%20delegates%20and%20visitors%20at%20the%20centre.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20earn%20an%20income%20from%20this%3B%20our%20goal%20is%20simply%20to%20help%20our%20farmer%20brothers%20earn%20extra%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anusuya%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20been%20working%20in%20the%20social%20development%20sector%20for%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20focusing%20on%20human%20rights.%20We%20were%20inspired%20to%20take%20up%20initiatives%20that%20boost%20the%20income%20of%20rural%20residents.%E2%80%9D%20Besides%20her%20role%20in%20the%20association%2C%20Anusuya%20also%20works%20as%20a%20translator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20innovative%20approach%20not%20only%20addresses%20the%20waste%20problem%20but%20also%20generates%20additional%20income%20for%20farmers.%20Currently%2C%20at%20least%201%2C000%20farmers%20across%20Kordha%2C%20Cuttack%2C%20and%20Puri%20districts%20of%20Odisha%20are%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20approach%20provides%20a%20valuable%20template%20for%20rural%20development%20and%20demonstrates%20the%20potential%20of%20waste-to-wealth%20initiatives%20in%20promoting%20sustainable%20agricultural%20practices%20and%20improving%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20rural%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kasinath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20every%20stem%2C%20we%20give%20Rs%2070-80%20to%20a%20farmer.%20By%20collecting%20waste%20from%20farm%20sites%2C%20we%20clean%20their%20field.%20This%20indirectly%20helps%20them%20as%20it%20saves%20them%20labour%20costs.%20On%20average%2C%20a%20farmer%20associated%20with%20us%20earns%20an%20additional%20Rs%207%2C000%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20for%20banana%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20